###
### Update Room Status
PUT {{baseUrl}}/rooms/1/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

"Available"

###
### ========== BOOKINGS - Đặt Phòng ==========

### Search Available Rooms
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings/search-room
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "checkInDate": "2026-03-25",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-03-27",
  "guestCount": 2,
  "roomTypeId": 1
}

###
### Get Available Physical Rooms
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/available-physical-rooms?roomTypeId=1&checkIn=2026-03-25&checkOut=2026-03-27

###
### Create Booking
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "roomId": 1,
  "checkInDate": "2026-03-25",
  "checkOutDate": "2026-03-27",
  "guestName": "Nguyễn Văn A",
  "guestEmail": "guest@example.com",
  "guestPhone": "0901234567",
  "totalPrice": 3000000
}

###
### Get My Bookings
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookings/my-bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Cancel Booking
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/bookings/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

