###
### ========== ATTRACTIONS ENHANCEMENTS ==========
### Soft Delete, Google Maps Integration, Cloudinary Image Storage

### 1. Create Attraction with Google Places Data and Base64 Image
POST {{baseUrl}}/attractions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tháp Trầm Hương - Nha Trang",
  "description": "Tháp cổ kính 9 tầng với kiến trúc châu Á đặc sắc, nằm trên đỉnh đồi Trầm Hương",
  "location": "Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa, Việt Nam",
  "googlePlaceId": "ChIJ7aFvPHNIVjARqnO_3zrGEcU",
  "latitude": 12.2427,
  "longitude": 109.2032,
  "mainImageBase64": "iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAEAAAABCAYAAAAfFcSJAAAADUlEQVR42mNk+M9QDwADhgGAWjR9awAAAABJRU5ErkJggg==",
  "imageUrls": ["https://example.com/image1.jpg", "https://example.com/image2.jpg"]
}

###
### 2. Get All Attractions (non-deleted only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attractions

###
### 3. Get Single Attraction with Images
GET {{baseUrl}}/attractions/1

###
### 4. Search Attractions by Google Places (Admin/Receptionist only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attractions/search/nhà%20thờ%20đá
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Alternative: Search with query parameter
GET {{baseUrl}}/attractions/search/cảng%20và%20bãi%20biển
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 5. Get Nearby Attractions (Google Maps - No Auth Required)
### Find tourist attractions within 5000 meters of Nha Trang center (12.2427, 109.2032)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attractions/nearby/12.2427/109.2032?radiusMeters=5000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 6. Update Attraction (with image management)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/attractions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Tháp Trầm Hương - Nha Trang [Cập nhật]",
  "description": "Tháp cổ kính 9 tầng với kiến trúc châu Á đặc sắc, nằm trên đỉnh đồi Trầm Hương. Nơi tuyệt vời để chụp ảnh lúc hoàng hôn.",
  "location": "Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa, Việt Nam",
  "googlePlaceId": "ChIJ7aFvPHNIVjARqnO_3zrGEcU",
  "latitude": 12.2427,
  "longitude": 109.2032,
  "mainImageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/your-cloud/image/upload/v1234567890/example.jpg",
  "imageUrlsToAdd": ["https://example.com/new-image1.jpg"],
  "imageIdsToRemove": [1]
}

###
### 7. Soft Delete Attraction (logical delete - IsDeleted = true)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/attractions/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 8. Verify Attraction is Soft Deleted (should not appear in list)
GET {{baseUrl}}/attractions

###
### 9. Restore Deleted Attraction (Admin Only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/attractions/1/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### 10. Verify Attraction is Restored
GET {{baseUrl}}/attractions/1

###
### ========== NOTES ==========
### 
### Authentication:
### 1. Get admin/receptionist token from /auth/login
### 2. Replace {{token}} with actual JWT token
### 
### Soft Delete Benefits:
### - Data is never permanently deleted
### - Can restore if needed
### - Maintains referential integrity
### - Supports audit trails
### 
### Google Maps Integration:
### - searchPlaces: Text search for attractions
### - nearbyPlaces: Find attractions near coordinates
### - getDetails: Fetch photos and ratings from Google
### 
### Cloudinary Image Storage:
### - Automatic image optimization (1200x800)
### - CDN delivery for faster loading
### - Store public IDs for future deletion
### 
### RBAC Permissions:
### - Public: List, Details, Nearby (no auth required)
### - Admin/Receptionist: Create, Update, Soft Delete
### - Admin Only: Restore deleted attractions

###
### Create Post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Khuyến mãi mùa hè",
  "content": "Giảm giá 20% cho booking trong tháng 6",
  "categoryId": 1
}

###
### Update Post
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Khuyến mãi mùa hè - Updated",
  "content": "Giảm giá 30% cho booking trong tháng 6",
  "categoryId": 1
}

###
### Delete Post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### ========== SERVICES - Dịch Vụ Thêm ==========

### Get All Services
GET {{baseUrl}}/services
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Order Service
POST {{baseUrl}}/services/order
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookingId": 1,
  "serviceId": 1,
  "quantity": 1,
  "requestedTime": "2026-03-25T18:00:00"
}

###
### ========== HR / RBAC - Nhân sự & Phân quyền ==========

### Get All Users (HR)
GET {{baseUrl}}/hr/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
### Assign Role to User
POST {{baseUrl}}/rbac/assign-role
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "roleId": 2
}

###
### Get User Permissions
GET {{baseUrl}}/rbac/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ========== NOTES ==========
# 1. Thay {{token}} bằng JWT token từ login response
# 2. Thay {{baseUrl}} nếu API chạy trên port khác
# 3. Sử dụng REST Client extension (REST Client by Huachao Mao) để chạy requests
# 4. Nhấp "Send Request" trên dòng đầu tiên của mỗi request
